1. *Samom* početku, znao sam da će biti teško. (At the very beginning, I knew it would be difficult.)
2. Ova knjiga je posvećena *samom* Vuku Karadžiću. (This book is dedicated to Vuk Karadzic himself.)
3. Ova zemlja je najplodnija upravo na *samom* jugu. (This land is most fertile right in the south itself.)
4. Čak i *sam* pomisao na to me plaši. (Even the thought itself scares me.)
5. *Samom* kraju godine, svi su umorni i spremni za odmor. (Towards the very end of the year, everyone is tired and ready for a break.)
6. Uživam u *samoj* tišini koju pruža priroda. (I enjoy the sheer silence that nature provides.)
7. Moramo razgovarati o ovome *samima* sa sobom. (We need to talk about this ourselves.)
8. Želim da napravim ovo *samom* sebi, bez tvoje pomoći. (I want to do this alone, without your help.)
9. *Samim* tim, ovaj problem postaje još ozbiljniji. (Therefore, this problem becomes even more serious.)
10. Zadovoljstvo mi je bilo biti *samom* dijelu ovog projekta. (It was my pleasure to be a part of this project myself.)